name: Robotezos #19
description:
EOSBOT x grasshopper

"EOSBOT" This robot is a robot with complex weapons, in every body there is a deadly weapon to fight the enemy. the top there is an x-ray, to detect the enemy, has spiked wings to avoid the rear attack. had pincers on his shoulders, and hands of a dragon, along with a sword. This robot is predicted to be one of the most feared robots
a change from a grasshopper, this robot has large hind legs that help them jump long distances from place to place, has two pairs of wings, with slender front wings and large hind wings. This robot can jump as far as 20 times its body length. keep up with the excitement of the Robotezos story and roadmap, on the official twitter account: https://twitter.com/robotezos and don't forget our NFT collection. who will mint with 1000 supply, and many other surprises
